&lt;p&gt;EBANX is one of the most successful fintechs to emerge from Latin America — and today, we are building a truly global payments company. Our mission has remained constant from day one: to unlock access and enable companies and consumers to participate in the digital economy, no matter where they are.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;What started as a bold vision has grown into a platform that connects some of the world’s largest digital businesses with customers across 21 of the fastest-growing markets. We operate where complexity exists — turning local challenges into global opportunities, and building the infrastructure that allows payments to move further, faster, and smarter.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We are a team of builders and problem-solvers. We think globally, act with curiosity, and believe diversity of thought is a competitive advantage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As EBANX enters its next phase of hyper growth, we are looking for people who want to shape the future of payments, expand what’s possible, and help connect businesses and consumers across borders.&lt;br&gt;Let’s build what’s next — together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At EBANX’s IT team you don’t just manage systems and infrastructure. You ensure that our technology, which connects millions of people to global companies, runs flawlessly every day. Here, every solution you create has a direct impact on the revolution of digital payments, making our work truly &lt;strong&gt;Out Of The Ordinary&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Corporate IT &amp;amp; Business Applications Senior Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to be part of a high growth technology and payments company with a solid track record of delivering high value to our customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What your day-to-day will look like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be responsible for the internal Business Applications team, partnering with functional areas, software engineering teams, project managers and external consulting partners;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the strategy, roadmap, operations and continuous improvement of SAP S/4HANA and other corporate business applications, ensuring availability, performance, security and business alignment;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish governance for enterprise applications, including lifecycle management, architecture standards and governance of internally developed and AI/Vibe-coded business solutions;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the Corporate IT function, overseeing network infrastructure, workplace technologies, service desk, help desk, end-user support and hardware and software asset management;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive service management excellence by managing incidents, requests, SLAs, knowledge management, automation and continuous improvement initiatives;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage software licensing, technology budgets, maintenance costs and vendor relationships, ensuring cost efficiency and value delivery;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage contracts and relationships with consulting firms, outsourcing providers and strategic technology partners;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the Technology Project Management function, defining priorities, governance, portfolio management and successful delivery of strategic technology initiatives;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong relationships with business leaders and other technology teams, acting as a trusted partner for digital transformation initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you need to shine in this role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading digital transformation initiatives and fostering a culture of innovation through emerging technologies, automation and AI adoption;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Broad experience across core IT functions, including Enterprise Applications, Infrastructure &amp;amp; Cloud, IT Operations, Service Management and IT Governance;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading multid

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;No &lt;strong&gt;EBANX&lt;/strong&gt;, acreditamos que barreiras foram feitas para serem quebradas. Começamos nossa história em Curitiba, Brasil, e hoje somos uma empresa global, presente em mais de &lt;strong&gt;29 países&lt;/strong&gt;, com escritórios em&lt;strong&gt; Curitiba,&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;São Paulo, Shanghai, Singapura e Johannesburg&lt;/strong&gt;. Ao todo são +&lt;strong&gt;700 ebankers&lt;/strong&gt; espalhados pelo mundo, conectando empresas como &lt;strong&gt;Uber, Netflix, Spotify, TikTok, Canva, Shopee, Meta, Shein &lt;/strong&gt;a milhões de consumidores em mercados emergentes, criando novas oportunidades e revolucionando o futuro dos pagamentos digitais.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Nossa missão é clara: &lt;strong&gt;dar acesso global para todos&lt;/strong&gt;. Somos guiados pelo lema #TamoJunto que se traduz em quatro grandes pilares: &lt;strong&gt;Shape Tomorrow, Evolve Fast, Make It Happen e Unlock The World&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Se você quer fazer parte de uma empresa global, com crescimento acelerado e que transforma o futuro dos pagamentos digitais, o EBANX é o lugar.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Como será o seu dia a dia&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead and coordinate strategic Cash Management projects within Treasury.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Act as PMO for Treasury initiatives, monitoring timelines, risks, dependencies, and action plans.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lead discussions and negotiations with local and global banking partners for the implementation of banking solutions and projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support the expansion and optimization of the company&#39;s banking infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Map, review, and optimize processes, workflows, and controls, driving efficiency, scalability, and risk mitigation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Serve as the key liaison between Treasury and other business areas to enable cross-functional projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop, document, and promote best practices, fostering standardization and governance across regions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Leverage data and performance indicators to support analysis, decision-making, and the identification of continuous improvement opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;O que você precisa ter para brilhar nessa função&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Business Administration, Economics, Engineering, Finance, Accounting, or related fields.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Advanced or fluent English.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Advanced or fluent Spanish.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous experience working in regional or global environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Knowledge of Cash Management products and operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience with SAP, Treasury Management Systems (TMS), and project management tools.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience in transformation, automation, and process standardization projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience in fintechs, payment services, or technology companies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Knowledge of banking connectivity solutions, including SWIFT, APIs, Host-to-Host, and SFTP.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proficiency in Artificial Intelligence and automation tools applied to productivity enhancement, information analysis, and process optimization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Diferenciais que podem contar

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;EBANX is one of the most successful fintechs to emerge from Latin America — and today, we are building a truly global payments company. Our mission has remained constant from day one: to unlock access and enable companies and consumers to participate in the digital economy, no matter where they are.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;What started as a bold vision has grown into a platform that connects some of the world’s largest digital businesses with customers across 21 of the fastest-growing markets. We operate where complexity exists — turning local challenges into global opportunities, and building the infrastructure that allows payments to move further, faster, and smarter.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We are a team of builders and problem-solvers. We think globally, act with curiosity, and believe diversity of thought is a competitive advantage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As EBANX enters its next phase of hyper growth, we are looking for people who want to shape the future of payments, expand what’s possible, and help connect businesses and consumers across borders.&lt;br&gt;Let’s build what’s next — together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Country Manager to strengthen our presence in South Cone and help shape the next stage of our growth in the country.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What your day-to-day will look like&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute the growth strategy for the South Cone market, aligning local priorities with EBANX’s regional and global objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify business opportunities, assess market trends, and build data-driven business cases that support sustainable growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain strategic relationships with merchants, banks, acquirers, payment providers, fintechs, regulators, and other key ecosystem stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the voice of the market internally, helping regional and global teams understand local opportunities, risks, customer needs, and competitive dynamics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and influence cross-functional initiatives across Sales, Product, Operations, Treasury, Finance, Legal, Regulatory, and Account Management teams to drive business outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor business performance, investigate root causes behind key metrics, and coordinate solutions for commercial, operational, or financial challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up to date with industry developments, regulatory changes, emerging payment solutions, and competitive movements across the region.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the continuous improvement of EBANX’s processes, ways of working, and use of technology, including AI-driven tools and solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you need to shine in this role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience in payments, fintech, financial services, digital commerce, or a closely related industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of the business landscape and payments ecosystem in Argentina and/or Chile.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to influence stakeholders and lead strategic initiatives without direct authority over teams or resources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical and problem-solving skills, with confidence working with business metrics, financial drivers, and data-driven decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commercial acumen and the ability to identify, evaluate, and pursue growth opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on mindset, with the ability to move seamlessly between strategic planning and operational execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and relationship-building skills in both Spanish and English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Bonus points if you have&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Portuguese language skill

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description for Country Manager, Turkey&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Location: Istambul, Turkey&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Background:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
