&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Operations:&lt;/strong&gt; Build and manage the operational infrastructure necessary to support our business growth, continuously optimizing our payment processes to boost efficiency and conversion rates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Forge Key Partnerships:&lt;/strong&gt; Identify, cultivate, and negotiate strategic relationships with Central Bank of Turkey,Troy,banks, acquirers, payment processors, and other key stakeholders to unlock new opportunities for growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate and Align:&lt;/strong&gt; Work closely with our expansion, product, technology, and legal teams to align on roadmaps and ensure seamless integration of partnerships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analyze and Optimize:&lt;/strong&gt; Use data and market insights to analyze performance, identify areas for improvement, and drive operational excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ensure Compliance:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate with our legal and compliance teams to ensure strict adherence to all local laws and regulations, staying up-to-date on any changes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Represent Our Brand:&lt;/strong&gt; Build and maintain a strong professional network, actively participating in industry events and organizations to enhance our brand presence in the market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
