&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;1,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Own the end-to-end execution of complex and strategic deals&lt;/strong&gt;, acting as the single point of coordination across all cross-functional stakeholders from commercials accepted to contract signed;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;1,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Maintain a real-time view of each deal&#39;s status&lt;/strong&gt;, next actions, owners, and blockers using Salesforce and project management tooling;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;1,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Drive deal reviews and status syncs with stakeholders&lt;/strong&gt;, keeping everyone accountable to deadlines without creating unnecessary operational overhead;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
