&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;1344&quot; data-end=&quot;1382&quot;&gt;What your day-to-day will look like&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Revenue Strategy Analyst will support the Head of Revenue Strategy in executing the Value Creation agenda within the Revenue organization - a cross-functional mandate sitting at the heart of the CRO&#39;s office. This is a high-visibility, high-impact role for someone who is analytical, organized and comfortable navigating ambiguity across multiple workstreams simultaneously.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In partnership with the leader, the ebanker will be responsible for bringing rigor, structure and execution quality to the day-to-day, ensuring projects move forward, insights are well-packaged and stakeholders are kept aligned.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project Execution &amp;amp; Orchestration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the orchestration of key cross-functional initiatives led by the CRO, tracking progress and flagging blockers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain project documentation, status updates and follow-up logs across active workstreams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with internal stakeholders — Sales, Finance, Product, FP&amp;amp;A — to ensure alignment and pace&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analysis &amp;amp; Insights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct ad-hoc commercial and financial analysis to support strategic decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain dashboards and reports that provide structured visibility on key initiatives and revenue metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research market trends, competitive dynamics and internal data to feed monetization and growth projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Executive Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help prepare materials for CRO-level and C-suite audiences — clear, structured and insight-driven&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Synthesize inputs from multiple sources into concise, decision-ready outputs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
