&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EBANX&lt;/strong&gt;, we connect global merchants to millions of consumers in emerging markets. Moving money across borders requires massive operational coordination across Revenue, Compliance, Engineering, Product and Operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re hiring an &lt;strong&gt;AI Solutions Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; for our Operations Transformation team. You won&#39;t be writing isolated code in a vacuum. Instead, you will embed directly with our core ops teams, shadow their workflows, pinpoint bottlenecks, and build the AI-driven automations and internal tools they need to run EBANX efficiently.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our environment bridges two worlds: you will design high-velocity, asynchronous AI systems in modern &lt;strong&gt;TypeScript/Node.js&lt;/strong&gt;, while safely reading from and optimizing our robust, legacy operational core built on &lt;strong&gt;PHP&lt;/strong&gt;. We need a pragmatic builder who respects legacy systems for the revenue they drive and knows how to leverage modernization without breaking the business.&lt;/p&gt;
