&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What your day-to-day will look like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;• Operational &amp;amp; Performance Ownership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Own the end-to-end operational health of key payment partners in Mexico, focusing on Cards and Alternative Payment Methods. Monitor and analyze KPIs such as approval rates, latency, transaction quality, settlement accuracy, and partner performance.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;• Technical &amp;amp; Analytical Point of Contact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Act as the main interface between EBANX and partner technical teams, supporting integrations, troubleshooting, and performance optimization with a strong technical and data-oriented mindset.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;• Data-Driven Optimization&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Analyze large datasets to identify trends, anomalies, and optimization opportunities. Propose and implement improvements in payment flows, routing logic, retries, and operational processes to increase approval rates and efficiency.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;• Advanced Analytics &amp;amp; AI (Plus)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Apply (or support the application of) advanced analytics, automation, or AI-driven approaches to improve payment performance, anomaly detection, fraud signals, and operational efficiency.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;• Partner Performance &amp;amp; Continuous Improvement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Lead Root Cause Analysis (RCA) processes with partners and internal teams, ensuring structured follow-ups and implementation of preventive actions based on data insights.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;• KPI Ownership &amp;amp; Data Visualization&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Define, track, and own key operational KPIs. Work closely with Data teams to build dashboards, automate reporting, and deliver clear data visualizations to support decision-making.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;• Strategic Insights &amp;amp; Business Intelligence&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Translate operational and performance data into actionable insights for Product, Finance, Country Growth, and Commercial teams, influencing strategy, pricing, and partner decisions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;• BEAT Report &amp;amp; Executive Communication&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Lead the creation and presentation of the BEAT (Benchmark, Evaluation, Action, Tracking) report, providing senior leadership with a clear, data-backed view of operational performance and improvement plans.

